author: cnbc.com
title: Lamb Weston Announces Details of Fiscal 2018 Third Quarter Earnings Release and Conference Call
text:
EAGLE, Idaho--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) will report its fiscal 2018 third quarter financial results on Thursday, April 5, 2018. The news release will be issued at approximately 8:30 a.m. EDT.
Lamb Weston will host a conference call Thursday, April 5, 2018, at 10 a.m. EDT to discuss the results. Participants in the U.S. and Canada may access the conference call toll-free by dialing 800-239-9838 and participants outside the U.S. and Canada should dial 01 800 062 2963. The event passcode is 8591354. The conference call also may be accessed live on the internet. Participants can register for the event here https://pgi.webcasts.com/starthere.jsp?ei=1186135&tp_key=1fa7682a86 .
A rebroadcast of the conference call will be available on Wednesday, April 5, after 2 p.m. EDT at https://investors.lambweston.com/events-and-presentations .
About Lamb Weston
Lamb Weston is a leading supplier of frozen potato, sweet potato, appetizer and vegetable products to restaurants and retailers around the world. For more than 60 years, Lamb Weston has led the industry in innovation, introducing inventive products that simplify back-of-house management for our customers and make things more delicious for their customers. From the fields where Lamb Weston potatoes are grown to proactive customer partnerships, Lamb Weston always strives for more and never settles. Because, when we look at a potato, we see possibilities. Learn more about us at lambweston.com .
